---
// AffiliateCard.astro
---

<div class="affiliate-card">
  <div class="card-tag">Nomad Gear Choice</div>
  <h4>Recommended Connectivity Hardware</h4>
  <p class="affiliate-desc">If the cell signal is reported as "Weak" or "Medium" at this park, we recommend using a high-gain signal booster or Starlink kit to ensure stable internet access.</p>
  
  <div class="gear-list">
    <div class="gear-item">
      <span class="gear-icon">📡</span>
      <div class="gear-info">
        <h5>weBoost Drive Reach RV</h5>
        <p>Best cellular signal booster for moving & stationary RVs. Boosts all US carriers by up to 32x.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="gear-item">
      <span class="gear-icon">🛰️</span>
      <div class="gear-info">
        <h5>Starlink Roam Kit</h5>
        <p>Best for remote sites with clear sky view. Connect anywhere with high-speed satellite broadband.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <a href="https://amazon.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm affiliate-btn">
    View Booster Kits on Amazon ↗
  </a>
  <span class="disclaimer">As an Amazon Associate we earn from qualifying purchases at no extra cost to you.</span>
</div>

<style>
  .affiliate-card {
    background-color: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .card-tag {
    position: absolute;
    top: var(--space-sm);
    right: var(--space-sm);
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 2px var(--space-sm);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .affiliate-card h4 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    max-width: 70%;
  }
  .affiliate-desc {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .gear-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  .gear-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .gear-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
  .gear-info h5 {
    margin: 0 0 2px 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .gear-info p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .affiliate-btn {
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .disclaimer {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
</style>
